metadata.name: Christmas Night with Dragon-Sikaco-chan! #1/150
metadata.description:
Merry Christmas!  
On Christmas Day, Dragon-Sikaco-chan's dragon blood will be awakened, and as a super dragon, he will continue to deliver heart-warming gifts all day long, burning away everyone's painful feelings from children to adults with his flames. Those who gaze upon her strong heart will be able to hold on to their happy feelings until next Christmas.  
We wish a happy Christmas to all.  
The first limited time edition, the first 30 people will receive a special stamp.
